    <!-- The About Section -->
    <div class="rowpg1" id="about">
        <div id="content-container">

            <div id="image-container">
                <img id="cropped-image" src="Images/wave-to-earth-fullPicture.png"
                     alt="Wave to Earth Members" title="Wave to Earth Members">
            </div>
    
            <div id="paragraph-container">
                <p>Based in Seoul, South Korea, 'Wave to Earth' is a three-member band consisting of Daniel Kim,
                    drummer Dong Kyu Shin, and bassist John Cha.
                </p>
                <p>'Wave to Earth' produces indie pop with a lo-fi sound based on jazz drumming, creating a unique sense of the
                    seasons and a dreamy atmosphere in the music.
                </p>
                <p>With the primary motto of "All Self-made," all recording, mixing, and mastering are done directly by the band
                    members, who also direct the overall art field, such as album art, video, and fashion.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div id="member1-image-container">
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/niellkim_/?hl=en" target="_blank">
